<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HPV Vaccine Survey - Form</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>HPV Vaccine Survey</h1>
    <p>This survey has received ethical approval and is anonymous. Your responses will help us understand HPV vaccine uptake among Hong Kong students.</p>
    <form action="/survey" method="POST">
      <!-- Section 1: Socio-Demographic Information -->
      <h2>Section 1: Socio-Demographic Information</h2>
      <div class="section">
        <label>Phone Number (Hong Kong, 8 digits):</label><br>
        <input type="tel" name="phoneNumber" pattern="[2356789][0-9]{7}" required placeholder="e.g., 91234567">
        <p class="note">Enter your 8-digit Hong Kong mobile number (starting with 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, or 9).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>Assigned 8-Digit ID:</label><br>
        <input type="text" name="assignedId" pattern="[0-9]{8}" required placeholder="e.g., 12345678">
        <p class="note">Enter the 8-digit ID assigned to you for this survey.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>A. Age:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="age" value="18" required> 18
        <input type="radio" name="age" value="19"> 19
        <input type="radio" name="age" value="20"> 20
        <input type="radio" name="age" value="21"> 21
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>B. Gender:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="gender" value="Female" required> Female
        <input type="radio" name="gender" value="Male"> Male
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>C. Studies:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="studies" value="HealthCare" required> Related to health care or biomedical science
        <input type="radio" name="studies" value="Other"> Other
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>D. Status:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="status" value="Single" required> Single
        <input type="radio" name="status" value="InRelationship"> In a relationship
        <input type="radio" name="status" value="Married"> Married
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>E. Family history of cancer:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="familyCancer" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="familyCancer" value="No"> No
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>F. Family or best friends who took HPV vaccine:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="friendsVaccine" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="friendsVaccine" value="No"> No
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>G. Residential:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="residential" value="HongKong" required> Hong Kong
        <input type="radio" name="residential" value="Kowloon"> Kowloon
        <input type="radio" name="residential" value="NewTerritories"> New Territories
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2: Knowledge about HPV -->
      <h2>Section 2: Knowledge about HPV</h2>
      <div class="section">
        <label>A. Please indicate your level of agreement:</label><br>
        <p>a. HPV is caused by a virus</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVirus" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVirus" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVirus" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVirus" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVirus" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>b. Most HPV-infected individuals show no symptoms and are unaware of their infection</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvNoSymptoms" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvNoSymptoms" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvNoSymptoms" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvNoSymptoms" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvNoSymptoms" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>c. HPV can lead to certain types of cancer such as cervical cancer</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCancer" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCancer" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCancer" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCancer" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCancer" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>d. The recommended age for HPV vaccination is 11 / 12 years</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAge" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAge" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAge" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAge" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAge" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>e. The use of condoms and dental dams can help prevent HPV transmission</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvPrevention" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvPrevention" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvPrevention" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvPrevention" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvPrevention" value="5"> Strongly agree
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>B. Please indicate if you agree or disagree:</label><br>
        <p>a. HPV is mainly transmitted by blood</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvBlood" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvBlood" value="No"> No

        <p>b. HPV is mainly transmitted via cough and aerosol droplets (respiratory system)</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvRespiratory" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvRespiratory" value="No"> No

        <p>c. HPV is mainly transmitted sexually through skin-to-skin contact and not through semen or body fluids</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSexual" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSexual" value="No"> No

        <p>d. Only women are at risk of HPV infection</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvWomenOnly" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvWomenOnly" value="No"> No

        <p>e. There is an existing treatment or cure for HPV</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCure" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCure" value="No"> No

        <p>f. An effective vaccine exists for HPV</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVaccineExists" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvVaccineExists" value="No"> No

        <p>g. There is a test available to detect HPV infection</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTest" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTest" value="No"> No
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3: Attitude towards HPV Vaccination -->
      <h2>Section 3: Attitude towards HPV Vaccination</h2>
      <div class="section">
        <label>A. In your opinion, HPV vaccination:</label><br>
        <p>Provides long-term protection against HPV infection (over 10 years)</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLongTerm" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLongTerm" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLongTerm" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLongTerm" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLongTerm" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Is effectively promoted by the Hong Kong government</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvGovPromotion" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvGovPromotion" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvGovPromotion" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvGovPromotion" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvGovPromotion" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Has a strong and efficient advertising campaign</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAdvertising" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAdvertising" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAdvertising" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAdvertising" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvAdvertising" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Can treat an HPV infection</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTreatInfection" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTreatInfection" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTreatInfection" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTreatInfection" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvTreatInfection" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Should be compulsory like COVID</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCompulsory" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCompulsory" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCompulsory" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCompulsory" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvCompulsory" value="5"> Strongly agree
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>B. Reasons for deciding to take the HPV vaccine:</label><br>
        <p>To comply with workplace/university requirements</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonWorkplace" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonWorkplace" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonWorkplace" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonWorkplace" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonWorkplace" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>To benefit from incentives promoting vaccination</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonIncentives" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonIncentives" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonIncentives" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonIncentives" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonIncentives" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>To follow recommendations from medical staff</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonMedical" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonMedical" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonMedical" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonMedical" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonMedical" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>To follow recommendations from family or friends</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyFriends" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyFriends" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyFriends" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyFriends" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyFriends" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>To protect myself against HPV and complications like cancer</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonProtect" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonProtect" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonProtect" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonProtect" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonProtect" value="5"> Strongly agree
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>C. Reasons for not receiving the HPV vaccine before:</label><br>
        <p>Vaccination is not deemed necessary due to low perceived risk of infection</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonLowRisk" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonLowRisk" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonLowRisk" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonLowRisk" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonLowRisk" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>The age factor is critical and young people do not need vaccination</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonAge" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonAge" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonAge" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonAge" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonAge" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Concerns about side effects or discomfort from injections</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSideEffects" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSideEffects" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSideEffects" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSideEffects" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSideEffects" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Vaccination is not compulsory by the government, school, or workplace</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNotCompulsory" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNotCompulsory" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNotCompulsory" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNotCompulsory" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNotCompulsory" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>The vaccine is too expensive</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonCost" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonCost" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonCost" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonCost" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonCost" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Lack of knowledge about HPV and the vaccination program</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNoKnowledge" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNoKnowledge" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNoKnowledge" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNoKnowledge" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonNoKnowledge" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Family opposition to vaccination</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyOpposition" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyOpposition" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyOpposition" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyOpposition" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonFamilyOpposition" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>Concerns regarding vaccine safety</p>
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSafety" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSafety" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSafety" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSafety" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="reasonSafety" value="5"> Strongly agree
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4: Comparison to Other Vaccines -->
      <h2>Section 4: Comparison to Other Vaccines</h2>
      <div class="section">
        <label>A. Have you received the following vaccines?</label><br>
        <p>Flu vaccine:</p>
        <input type="radio" name="fluVaccine" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="fluVaccine" value="No"> No
        <p>COVID vaccine:</p>
        <input type="radio" name="covidVaccine" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="covidVaccine" value="No"> No
        <p>Hepatitis vaccine:</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hepatitisVaccine" value="Yes" required> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="hepatitisVaccine" value="No"> No
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <label>B. In your opinion:</label><br>
        <p>a. The HPV vaccine may lead to more side effects than other vaccines</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSideEffects" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSideEffects" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSideEffects" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSideEffects" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvSideEffects" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>b. The HPV vaccine is less protective than other vaccines</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessProtective" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessProtective" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessProtective" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessProtective" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessProtective" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>c. The HPV vaccine is more expensive than other vaccines</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvExpensive" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvExpensive" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvExpensive" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvExpensive" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvExpensive" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>d. HPV disease is less common and less dangerous than other diseases</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessDangerous" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessDangerous" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessDangerous" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessDangerous" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLessDangerous" value="5"> Strongly agree

        <p>e. There is a lack of information and knowledge about HPV</p>
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLackInfo" value="1" required> Strongly disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLackInfo" value="2"> Disagree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLackInfo" value="3"> Neutral
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLackInfo" value="4"> Agree
        <input type="radio" name="hpvLackInfo" value="5"> Strongly agree
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit Survey</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
